      <akn:section eId="sec_32_1231_08">
        <akn:num>32-1231.08</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Hearing by Office of Administrative Hearings.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-1231_08_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>In accordance with ยง 2-1831.03(b)(1), a party contesting the determination made by DOES shall be entitled to a hearing before the Office of Administrative Hearings.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-1231_08_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Upon the exhaustion of administrative remedies, an employee aggrieved by the order of the Office of Administrative Hearings may bring an action in court.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
